{"tid":264242,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母！識飛既甲由痴撚線架！","createTime":"2017-05-30T15:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T17:48:17.000Z","uid":72608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"029fb5fc71f7bd4e49b64407eaed91b14085e7d6","tid":264242,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:55:05.000Z","msg":"又細隻又飛得高<br />\n一路飛，飛左唔知去邊<br />\n原來係飛左去書櫃底<br />\n咁我比Ｄ力去壓佢啦，但係生命力好強，壓唔撚死<br />\n佢而家被壓住但一直拍翼，啪啪聲，好撚嘈，好撚恐怖呀屌，點樣殺佢好？<br />\n我諗識飛既甲由應該係當年上帝創造出黎，人類既天敵！屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec26abebab627ecb6679acbf6f866bacd4ab46f","tid":264242,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"原來個櫃底D空間唔夠壓死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢而家好似困左係果個空間裡面<br />\n總之好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解甲由會識飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌拿聲訓教唔撚理，我訓緊果陣唔好飛上黎就得！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"3295596fbbb24ff91a911c26bdc8f8d36a5b95ae","tid":264242,"uid":42625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:58:55.000Z","msg":"我為咗避佢地買咗個蚊帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f356f26688697eaa33418fd5dfe7bdcce2f69ea2","tid":264242,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"希望佢飛入樓豬個口度"},{"pid":"b39067b028705a505104ae1a311ad387139c3b03","tid":264242,"uid":8304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"用愛膚堅啦"},{"pid":"c6084515c07ec16fcd11c69efd0721711ae6c7bc","tid":264242,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:11:13.000Z","msg":"係咪傻的嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直唔明點解有人可以唔打死佢 雖然驚啫 但無理由畀佢喺到通屋走 你瞓咗教佢想點都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbba7f06a9f07